title: HOUR 1- Ross Tucker Oct 20, 2020

description:
Ross Tucker says the conditions were not that bad for the Chiefs and Bills game, but he does think the weather was a factor. Ross says he is disappointed in Josh Allen. Ross tells Dan that every where he goes; people are always asking him if Josh Allen is for real.
